2. The 1st day of May 2024 is appointed as the day on which the 
European Arrest Warrant (Amendment) Act 2024 (No. 9 of 2024) shall come 
into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

30 April, 2024. 

HELEN MCENTEE, 
Minister for Justice. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 3rd May, 2024.
